  "subject": "[APPC-44] APPC Lifecycle Management refactor",
  "commit_message": "[APPC-44] APPC Lifecycle Management refactor\n\nPull APPC lifecycle Management out of APPC dispatcher, so that it can be\nused by both APPC dispatcher and APPC OAM. This is the pre-step of\nintroducing APPC OAM operations.\n\nIssue-Id: APPC-44\nChange-Id: Icbde399b5121fae9e1919cfdd5c77bbe55d61188\nSigned-off-by: beili.zhou <beili.zhou@amdocs.com>\n\n[APPC-44] update for review comments\n\nUpdate based on review comments, and added feature dependency on\nappc-common in APPC lifecycle management\n\nIssue-Id: APPC-44\nChange-Id: If0439ac0f1013cdc8a9d8fb0a672c1b7695ace07\nSigned-off-by: beili.zhou <beili.zhou@amdocs.com>\n",
